    text "(a) Short title; Congressional declaration of intent"
  ]
  node [
    id 708
    label "section_652_subsection_a_item_1"
    class_name "item"
    text "(1) This section may be cited as the &#8220;Upper Mississippi River Management Act of 1986&#8221;."
  ]
  node [
    id 709
    label "section_652_subsection_a_item_2"
    class_name "item"
    text "(2) To ensure the coordinated development and enhancement of the Upper Mississippi River system, it is hereby declared to be the intent of Congress to recognize that system as a nationally significant ecosystem and a nationally significant commercial navigation system. Congress further recognizes that the system provides a diversity of opportunities and experiences. The system shall be administered and regulated in recognition of its several purposes."
  ]
